p: The data are expressed as mean ± standard error of the mean (SE). The differences among groups were analyzed using a one-way ANOVA after the extraction of all 26 constituents versus the concurrent constituents present in each of the oil sample. Similarly, differences among groups was analyzed using a two-way ANOVA after the antioxidant test was performed. A post hoc test was performed using Tukey’s multi-group comparison on GraphPad Prism 8.0.2. The significance value was set at p < 0.05.
